{"tid":1045714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"MK妹係咪已經絕曬種","createTime":"2019-03-03T18:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T09:39:10.000Z","uid":72226,"like":110,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ad2046b22b09164d3b631841e1da6d3031dd6eb1","tid":1045714,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T18:07:41.000Z","msg":"近呢一兩年成日出街都唔見有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而見到周街都係偽韓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係就大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好懷念以前中學時代嗰啲斜陰MK妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話MK都好吹奏 我都係咁話<br />\nMk假假地都香港本土文化<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再係咁落去過多10年 都已經冇人知道Mk呢兩個字點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後請大家珍惜MK妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMk妹示意圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/020331_49666198f1c412a94a661de9c51ef65b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F020331_49666198f1c412a94a661de9c51ef65b.png&h=ab6883ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n偽韓狗示意圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/020407_0f937859e48522c2a2eb45c5d4f444b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F020407_0f937859e48522c2a2eb45c5d4f444b3.png&h=f5fe2eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMK妺:正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n偽韓妹:負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/n